{"tid":2342339,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple 私隱保護計劃現身 iOS 14.4    是否接受追蹤廣告可自己決定","createTime":"2020-12-27T05:04:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T14:43:28.000Z","uid":105678,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cc3c3b0291bc07cdd414a14928060117042f9073","tid":2342339,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T05:04:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/freBPKk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfreBPKk.jpg&h=ad8ea5c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nApple 早前宣布會在 iOS 14 新增私隱保護計劃，以限制 App 蒐集可用於目標式廣告的手機資訊。據正試用 iOS 14.4 Beta 版的開發者表示，該私隱保護計劃已開始啟動並進行測試，預計明年年初會正式推出予用戶更新。<br />\n<br />\nApple 表示，將會為 iOS 14 新增私隱保護設計，在用戶安裝新 App 時彈出通知，詢問用戶是否準許 App 追蹤其資訊。而其亦已提醒 iPhone 和 iPad App 留意，iOS 系統將向用戶提供控制個性化廣告跟蹤的權利，並在上同發布的 iOS 14.4 Beta 中推出相關功能。<br />\n<br />\n據指，Apple 原計劃在本年 9 月推出此功能，但為了給開發者提供更多的時間準備時間，推遲了正式公開期限，現預計 iOS 14.4 應該會在明年 1 月或 2 月公開給所有用戶使用。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：macrumors"},{"pid":"287006cb4438edc5cba7dfbad1f323557940ccc0","tid":2342339,"uid":164092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T05:26:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FP9NWwU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFP9NWwU.png&h=47a0c703&s={SIZE}\" />有咩分別？"},{"pid":"72c6b811aac4c3a75541a29985b3957569f865bd","tid":2342339,"uid":168366,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T05:55:26.000Z","msg":"Fb玩撚完"},{"pid":"237a9a97c3f877a192ef75cb532e22a8b06ec174","tid":2342339,"uid":106,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T06:29:58.000Z","msg":"希望可以收FB皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b931647d82910e89ec19994db090fa8445bc78e4","tid":2342339,"uid":7198,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T07: